data.description:
Network configuration and change management (NCCM) is a discipline in information technology. According to research from IDC and Gartner, NCCM is one of the fastest growing markets in the ITOM market. Organizations are using NCCM as a way to:automate changes;
reduce network downtime;
network device configuration backup & restore;
meet compliance.

